Type: Package
Package: wdi2
Title: Download Indicators from the World Bank Indicators API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Christoph", "Scheuch", , "christoph.scheuch@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-0423-6819"))
  )
Description: The 'wdi2' package provides a modern, flexible interface for accessing the World Bankâ€™s
  World Development Indicators (WDI). Similar to the existing 'WDI' package, 'wdi2' allows users to 
  download, process, and analyze indicator data for multiple countries and years. However, 'wdi2' 
  differs by relying on 'httr2' for multi-page request and error handling, providing support for 
  downloading multiple indicators with a single function call, using progress bars to keep users 
  informed about the data processing, and returning the processed data in a tidy data format.
